    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Once you get started there's no stopping your momentum. Once per turn, if you hit a creature with a melee Taijutsu attack after moving at least 30 feet, spend 10 chakra and deal an additional 4d8 damage. If you activate this jutsu again the following turn increase the chakra cost by 5 chakra and the bonus damage by an additional 2d8, up to a max of 12d8 bonus damage. This damage and chakra cost resets if you go a turn without casting it.</p>",
